{"tid":106432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死1隻]村民放煙花　誤炸毀樓房一人亡","createTime":"2017-02-03T16:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T16:33:43.000Z","uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"02c2f8f24f30be2b19c36c14d3c97a3131fa3410","tid":106432,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T16:10:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170203/bkncn-20170203084233995-0203_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170203%2Fbkncn-20170203084233995-0203_05011_001.html&d=WPnlDqr2f%2BBS7HOcP0JQkzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=18927b62\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170203/bkncn-20170203084233995-0203_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170203/photo/bkncn-20170203084233995-0203_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170203%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170203084233995-0203_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=237afdb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地多個城市在新春期間禁放或限放煙花炮仗，除減少污染外，亦為防止意外發生。惟四川宜賓江安縣鐵清鎮新廟村一戶人家，年三十除夕晚在燃放煙花時，將囤於屋內的煙花點着，導致兩層樓房被炸塌，在樓下看電視的30歲男子郭華（化名）被砸死，郭妻受傷，且致兩家鄰居房屋受損。<br />\n<br />\n事發除夕夜晚上約8時，村民趙達貴家親友多人在門口燃放鞭炮慶祝，「突然傳來巨響，人都站立不穩。」當地居民稱，事後眾人聞訊趕至，發現趙達貴家的二層樓房塌了一半，現場爆炸聲不斷，而且濃煙滾滾無法靠近，立即報警。當地消防出動3輛消防車、22名人員趕赴現場救援。<br />\n<br />\n消防到場發現，倒塌房屋為兩層磚混結構民房，地下為商舖，一樓為住宅，倒塌面積約90多平方米，隨即調集大型挖土機協助救援，同時疏散圍觀群眾。至翌日凌晨零時50分許，現場廢墟被清理完畢，救出一名被壓者，惟證實死亡。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，死者郭華是趙達貴哥哥的女婿，事發時郭華正在樓下看電視，趙家約20人在門外放煙花。為保證安全，當時還專門關好門面的捲簾門，但煙花衝力巨大，意外衝進門面內，引爆自家留存待放的另外20枚煙花，兩層高的樓房瞬間被震垮，樓板將郭華壓住。由於涉事雙方是親屬，善後事宜由雙方協商解決。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28070e5654885a4a953959430c1b90499b7509fb","tid":106432,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T16:29:08.000Z","msg":"由於涉事雙方是親屬，善後事宜由雙方協商解決。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"866735d48ecd98f27c725deb532fe40b84270fe5","tid":106432,"uid":7355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T16:33:43.000Z","msg":"friendly fire<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}